data.title: Prime Video: The Aristocats (Includes Bonus Features)
data.meta_description: A pedigreed cat and her three kittens are catnapped by a greedy butler who hopes to gain the inheritance left to them. Things look hopeless until they are befriended by Thomas O'Malley, an easy-going alley cat.
data.text:
The Aristocats (Includes Bonus Features)

A pedigreed cat and her three kittens are catnapped by a greedy butler who hopes to gain the inheritance left to them. Things look hopeless until they are befriended by Thomas O'Malley, an easy-going alley cat.

IMDb 7.12 h 3 min1970

ALL
